{"tid":2313412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國總統特朗普下令美軍撤出索馬里","createTime":"2020-12-05T18:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T05:26:19.000Z","uid":295230,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"784e2113b4a737cc0917bacf600576a34f667987","tid":2313412,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T18:13:48.000Z","msg":"按美國特朗普總統的指示，五角大樓周五晚對外宣布了美軍從索馬里撤出約700人的決定。<br />\n<br />\n美國目前有700名特種部隊的軍人在索馬里軍隊中擔任反恐顧問。美國國防部周五晚宣布了在2021年元月初，特朗普總統離任之前，從索馬里撤軍的決定。<br />\n<br />\n本台RFI記者Anne.C周六（2020年12月5日）發自華盛頓的報道說，五角大樓在一份聲明中明確表示，美國既不是解除契約，也不是退出非洲。美方依然履行其對非洲夥伴的承諾，為他們提供長久的支持。美國承諾保持其在索馬里開展反恐行動的能力。美國將保留其在肯尼亞和吉布提的軍事基地，美國的無人機從那裡起飛執行在索馬里的打擊。<br />\n<br />\n另據美國國防部消息，目前被派往索馬里的700名美軍，其中一部分未來將調離東非地區，另一部分則將依然留在附近。但美軍撤出後，索馬里軍隊將失去特種部隊的培訓。而且是在索馬里立法選舉之前一個月。分析人士擔心，索馬里立法選舉競選期間的恐怖襲擊活動將加劇。"},{"pid":"24a3e733c27e8b3dafae47f5faa52c74db69ce45","tid":2313412,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T18:20:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2/20201205-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E6%92%A4%E5%87%BA%E7%B4%A2%E9%A6%AC%E9%87%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%2F20201205-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%2587%258C&d=3iOM3afBfBP%2FWcaFgxWQowpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=a81bfc11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2/20201205-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A4%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E6%92%A4%E5%87%BA%E7%B4%A2%E9%A6%AC%E9%87%8C</a>"},{"pid":"f4021d90f7f1e77b4b91dfee9a972808efbdff9c","tid":2313412,"uid":70487,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T18:20:51.000Z","msg":"非洲有一帶一路，唔驚！"},{"pid":"32f53636c9b93a7154848df8cccfff0c783d5999","tid":2313412,"uid":301820,"like":12,"dislike":16,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T20:05:07.000Z","msg":"故事發生係索馬里<br />\n<br />\n海盜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n美軍終於走啦，係時候再食大茶飯<br />\n<br />\n海盜<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n支那人引走晒美軍，我哋今次有運行啦<br />\n<br />\n一眾海盜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：搶佢老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二日索馬里沿海<br />\n<br />\n海盜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: <br />\n前方發現商船，準備火箭炮、AK上船搶嘢<br />\n海盜<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/shaking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: <br />\n大哥，你都知我眼力比其他人好，<br />\n我發覺天上有新品種大鳥跟左我哋1日<br />\n<br />\n海盜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <br />\n唔好留意埋D 唔重要既嘢啦，準備登船搶嘢<br />\n<br />\n眾海盜<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喊：<br />\n前面既商船聽住，我哋係索馬里海盜<br />\n即刻投降，唔肯就用火箭炮射鳩你<br />\n<br />\n突然間，海盜船爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMQ-9又一次命中目標，索馬里海上又回復寧靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4f34d266c93e59b5a6717f5d4e857e9ee4b706","tid":2313412,"uid":370352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32f53636c9b93a7154848df8cccfff0c783d5999","tid":2313412,"uid":301820,"like":12,"dislike"